The clinical and cost effectiveness of cognitive behavioural therapy plus 
treatment as usual for the treatment of depression in advanced cancer (CanTalk): 
study protocol for a randomised controlled trial.

Serfaty M(1), King M(2), Nazareth I(3), Tookman A(4)(5), Wood J(3), Gola A(6), 
