An Occupational Therapy intervention for residents with stroke-related 
disabilities in UK Care Homes (OTCH): cluster randomised controlled trial with 
economic evaluation.

Sackley CM(1), Walker MF(2), Burton CR(3), Watkins CL(4), Mant J(5), Roalfe 
AK(6), Wheatley K(7), Sheehan B(8), Sharp L(9), Stant KE(6), Fletcher-Smith 
J(2), Steel K(10), Barton GR(9)(11), Irvine L(9), Peryer G(9); OTCH 
