Author information:
(1)Academic Department of Physiotherapy, School of Bioscience Education, Faculty 
of Life Sciences and Medicine, King's College London, London, UK.
(2)Division of Rehabilitation and Ageing, Faculty of Medicine and Health 
Sciences, University of Nottingham, Nottingham, UK.
